					"value": "Looping ADs between two duergar supervising some deep rothe that are being used to clear rubble. The duergar react to three main states: the rothe aren't working, after being scared by something, the rothe are dead, and the rothe have been calmed. The duergar are grim and vicious - certainly not concerned about animal welfare."
